      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical work to be roadworthy again. The engine has major performance issues, including a persistent knock and heavy oil consumption, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, there is noticeable rust on the rocker panels and several large dents on the passenger side. This car is ideal for someone looking for a major restoration project or a donor vehicle for parts.",
