    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and it's honestly been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really great shape and has been well-cared for over the years, so it's totally ready to hit the road with you today! It drives smoothly and looks wonderful, perfect for someone who wants a quality ride without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and go for a test drive!",
