    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion for me and is still in really wonderful shape\u2014definitely well-loved and ready for many more adventures. It's clean, runs smoothly, and has been super dependable. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car has got plenty of life left in it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
