      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L straight-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This unit delivers exceptional power through a Getrag 6-speed manual and a limited-slip differential. The chassis is sorted with reinforced subframe mounts and refreshed suspension bushings for precise turn-in and high-speed stability. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and VANOS system inspection, ensuring the double-VANOS variable valve timing remains optimal. A true driver\u2019s car with a visceral, analog feel and a well-sorted drivetrain.",
